trans-unit.source: Represents a collection of the <xref href="System.IdentityModel.Protocols.WSTrust.RequestClaim"></xref> objects inside <xref href="System.IdentityModel.Protocols.WSTrust.RequestSecurityToken"></xref>.
Represents the contents of the wst:Claims element.
trans-unit.target: 表示 wst:Claims 元素的内容。

trans-unit.source: This optional element requests the set of specific claim types requested by the client.
trans-unit.target: 这一可选元素请求客户端请求的特定的声明类型的集。

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.IdentityModel.Protocols.WSTrust.RequestClaimCollection.Dialect%2A> property specifies dialect of the <xref:System.IdentityModel.Protocols.WSTrust.RequestClaim> objects in the collection.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.IdentityModel.Protocols.WSTrust.RequestClaimCollection.Dialect%2A>属性指定的方言<xref:System.IdentityModel.Protocols.WSTrust.RequestClaim>集合中的对象。</xref:System.IdentityModel.Protocols.WSTrust.RequestClaim> </xref:System.IdentityModel.Protocols.WSTrust.RequestClaimCollection.Dialect%2A>

trans-unit.source: For more information about the element that this class represents, see the version of the WS-Trust specification that applies to your scenario.
trans-unit.target: 有关此类表示的元素的详细信息，请参阅适用于你的方案的 Ws-trust 规范的版本。

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.IdentityModel.Protocols.WSTrust.RequestClaimCollection"></xref> class.

After initialization, the <xref:System.IdentityModel.Protocols.WSTrust.RequestClaimCollection> is empty and the <xref:System.IdentityModel.Protocols.WSTrust.RequestClaimCollection.Dialect%2A> property is set to "http://schemas.xmlsoap.org/ws/2005/05/identity".
trans-unit.target: 初始化之后，<xref:System.IdentityModel.Protocols.WSTrust.RequestClaimCollection>为空和<xref:System.IdentityModel.Protocols.WSTrust.RequestClaimCollection.Dialect%2A>属性设置为"http://schemas.xmlsoap.org/ws/2005/05/identity"。</xref:System.IdentityModel.Protocols.WSTrust.RequestClaimCollection.Dialect%2A> </xref:System.IdentityModel.Protocols.WSTrust.RequestClaimCollection>

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the Dialect attribute.
trans-unit.target: 获取或设置的方言属性。

trans-unit.source: Represents the Dialect attribute of the wst:Claims element.
trans-unit.target: 表示 wst:Claims 元素的方言属性。

trans-unit.source: This required attribute contains a URI that indicates the syntax used to specify the set of requested claims.
trans-unit.target: 此必需的特性包含一个 URI，指示用于指定的请求的声明集的语法。

trans-unit.source: A string that contains the URI that identifies the dialect.
trans-unit.target: 包含用于标识方言的 URI 的字符串。

trans-unit.source: The default value is <xref:System.IdentityModel.Protocols.WSIdentity.WSIdentityConstants.Dialect>, which indicates that <xref href="System.IdentityModel.Protocols.WSTrust.RequestClaim"></xref> objects in the collection correspond to the Information Card profile.
trans-unit.target: 默认值是<xref:System.IdentityModel.Protocols.WSIdentity.WSIdentityConstants.Dialect>，这指示<xref href="System.IdentityModel.Protocols.WSTrust.RequestClaim"></xref>集合中的对象对应于信息卡配置文件。</xref:System.IdentityModel.Protocols.WSIdentity.WSIdentityConstants.Dialect>
